*Budete* li uspeli da završite zadatak u roku? (Will you be able to finish the task on time?)

*Budete* li otišli u šetnju? (Will you go for a walk?)

*Budu* li uspešni, biće to dobra vest. (If they are successful, it will be good news.)

*Budemo* li imali vremena, obići ćemo mnoge gradove. (If we have time, we will visit many cities.)

*Budu* li svi prisutni, počećemo sastanak. (If everyone is present, we will start the meeting.)

*Budete* li u mogućnosti da dođete ranije? (Will you be able to come earlier?)